SICCSPageTitle: CY-Check the SIC codes for this limited partnership
SICCSTableHeader: CY-Check the SIC codes and update any that have changed.
SICCSAddSICInsetInstructions: CY-Start typing a keyword to see a list of business activities. For example, 'finance'. Or, enter the SIC code if you know it.
SICCSWhatIsDetailExpanderParagraph1: CY-The SIC (Standard Industrial Classification) codes indicate the partnership's nature of business. A partnership can have up to 4 codes.
SICCSWhatIsDetailExpanderParagraph2: CY-Search for a business activity using keywords that best describe what the partnership does. If you can't find an exact match, search for other keywords that relate to the partnership's activities.
SICCSWhatIsDetailExpanderParagraph3Link: CY-SIC codes list (opens in a new tab)
SICCSWhatIsDetailExpanderParagraph3End: CY-may help you find a suitable business activity.
